text: The South Africa women's cricket team toured Australia in 1998–99, playing three women's One Day Internationals. Australia won the series 2-0, with the third match abandoned without a ball being bowled. ==One Day International series== ===1st ODI=== ===2nd ODI=== ===3rd ODI=== ==References== Category:1999 in South African cricket Category:1999 in South African women's sport Category:1999 in women's cricket Category:1998–99 Australian women's cricket season Category:February 1999 sports events in Oceania Category:International cricket competitions from 1997–98 to 2000 Australia 1998-99 Women 1998-99 South Africa 1998-99
